-- Russia's Putin says will not intervene in Bashneft probe
-- By Polina Devitt and Vladimir Soldatkin
-- Thu Oct 02, 2014 07:16AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 2 (Reuters) - Russian President Vladimir Putin said on Thursday that he will not intervene in the legal investigation into the privatisation of mid-sized oil producer Bashneft <BANE.MM>, controlled by the Sistema <AFKS.MM> conglomerate.

